Source of information:
===============================================================================
9 day Weather forecast: http://www.hko.gov.hk/textonly/v2/forecast/nday.htm

Could obtain - Date
             - Wind
               - Direction
               - Level
             - Weather
             - Temperature Range ( Unit: Degree Celsius )
               - Lowest
               - Highest 
             - R.H Range ( Unit: Percent )
               - Lowest
               - Highest



Regional Weather in Hong Kong: http://www.hko.gov.hk/textonly/v2/forecast/text_readings_e.htm

Could obtain - Location
             - Current Temperature
             - Relative Humidity
             - Min Temperature
             - Max Temperature
             - Past 24-Hour Temperature Difference
             - 10 minutes Mean Wind information
               - Direction
               - Speed
               - Max Gust
